---
By: P. T. Barnum
Source:
  ID: 57c5499b-c3b2-4b09-92a9-a6e977a32050
  Locus:
    Page: 232
    Verse: 19
Tags:
  - Health
---
The foundation of success in life is good health; that is the substratum
of fortune; it is also the basis of happiness. A person cannot accumulate
a fortune very well when he is sick. He has no ambition; no incentive;
no force.
